description: Trystan Bull has just finished tuning up his ATV in the garage. He's got it looking sharp, running in tip-top condition, and spit-shine clean. Of course, doing all of this has him a bit worked up, so he takes his shirt off to cool down. Maybe its the thought of all that power between his legs, but for whatever reason, in no time at all Trystan is all hot and bothered, and so he decides to just strip and take care of his raging hard-on right there in the garage.Enjoy!
title: In The Garage
